0.1.2 (May 2021)
*****************

Fixed an issue decoding the request body for HTTP methods like
POST, PUT, etc.


0.1.0 (Jan 2021)
*****************

Initial alpha release of the OpenAPI 3 plugin for
Bottle. Most functionality should be implemented.

